Uses of Package
com.flyingspaniel.net.weather

  • Packages that use com.flyingspaniel.net.weather 
    Package Description
    com.flyingspaniel.net.weather  
  • Classes in com.flyingspaniel.net.weather used by com.flyingspaniel.net.weather 
    Class and Description
    Condition
    Class representing weather conditions at a particular instant in time
    Forecast
    Class representing a weather forecast for a single day
    NDFD
    Represents (some) of the possible National Digital Forecast Database Element Names
    NDFDSeries
    Represents a time-series of NDFD measurements, which are linked to a TimeLayout
    NOAAWeather
    Implementation of IWeather using the NOAA National Weather Service
    NOAAWeather.MoreInfoKeys
    Keys for the moreInfo map.
    TimeInterval
    Represents an immutable interval of time (using longs for ms since Jan 1 1970) Most methods have two forms, one taking a long (and ending in "MS"), the other a non-null Date
    TimeLayout
    Represents a single TimeLayout from the NOAA weather REST API
    Weather.Interface
    Interface for classes that predict the weather (usually by asking somebody online) Classes should implement Callable and return themselves
